  "description": "<h1>Oslo</h1>\n<h3>OSL · 1.0.0</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Subway-Builder-Modded/registry/refs/heads/main/maps/oslo-no/gallery/screenshot1.webp\" alt=\"Map Preview\"></p>\n<h2>Coverage</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Bounding box</strong></td><td>9.55281, 58.98591, 11.48047, 60.41209</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Playable Area</strong></td><td>~17,000 km²</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Population Summary</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Total Modeled Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">1,649,396</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Modeled Normal Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">1,453,296</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Modeled Special Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">196,100</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Map Statistics</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Demand Points</strong></td><td align=\"right\">25,357</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Populations</strong></td><td align=\"right\">73,600</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Special Demand</h2>\n<details>\n<summary>Airports — 39,700</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;OSL&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;37,000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;TRF&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;2700&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Universities — 110,400</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;University of Oslo (UiO)&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;26,800&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Oslo Metropolitan University Pilestredet Campus&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;19,800&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Oslo Metropolitan University Kjeller Camp